OL,3,CBuilder jailed for hammer murder of
OL,4,Cwoman after 'disagreement'
OL,6,FA builder has been jailed after using
OL,7,Fa hammer to murder a woman whose house
OL,8,Fhe was working in.
OL,10,FPeter Norgrove, aged 43, pleaded
OL,11,Fguilty to the murder of 58-year-old
OL,12,FSharon Gordon at her home in .
OL,14,FMrs Gordon's body was found at the
OL,15,Ffoot of her staircase on Friday 21
OL,16,FJuly 2023, with "severe" head injuries
OL,17,Fafter her friends became concerned
OL,18,Fwhen she didn't turn up for work. She
OL,19,Fhad died the day before.
