OL,6,FNorgrove had met Mrs Gordon through
OL,7,Fmutual friends at the church they both
OL,8,Fattended.
OL,10,FThe recently-qualified bricklayer had
OL,11,Fbeen working on an extension at Mrs
OL,12,FGordon's home, which police say "had
OL,13,Ftaken many months" and "encountered
OL,14,Fseveral problems along the way."
OL,16,FNorgrove was interviewed by police and
OL,17,Fsaid he had left the property the
OL,18,Fprevious day.
