OL,6,FBut blood-stained items were found in
OL,7,Fa wheelie bin at a family address -
OL,8,Fand searches found a hammer hidden in
OL,9,Fa shed. He pleaded guilty to her
OL,10,Fmurder at Crown Court on December 4
OL,11,F2023.
OL,13,FOn Wednesday 31 January, Norgrove was
OL,14,Fsentenced to life in prison with a
OL,15,Fminimum term of 15 years.
