OL,6,FThe "rights and wrongs" of the
OL,7,Fextension over-run, which was more
OL,8,Fthan a year behind schedule, were not
OL,9,Fmatters for the court to determine,
OL,10,Fthe judge said.
OL,12,FHe added: "They do not provide you
OL,13,Fwith any excuse, justification or
OL,14,Fmitigation for what you did."
OL,16,FMs Gordon was found dead a day after
OL,17,Fthe killing by two friends who visited
OL,18,Fthe property, having been attacked
OL,19,Fbetween 2.01pm and 2.21pm on July 20
OL,20,F2023.
