OL,6,FProsecutor Earl Pinnock told the court
OL,7,Fthat camera footage showed Norgrove
OL,8,Fentering the property through the back
OL,9,Fdoor wearing rubber gloves.
OL,11,FMr Pinnock told the court: "At 14.02
OL,12,Fthe Ring doorbell recorded noises.
OL,13,FThey last for a duration of 18 seconds.
OL,15,F"A female voice screamed momentarily
OL,16,Fand then shouted something inaudible."
OL,18,FFootage recovered by police, which was
OL,19,Fissued after the sentencing, then
OL,20,Fcaught Norgrove leaving the property
OL,21,Fwith red marks on his trousers.
