OL,6,FDuring sentencing, Judge Chambers said
OL,7,FMrs Gordon may have lived for up to an
OL,8,Fhour after the attack, and told
OL,9,FNorgrove: "You went into the house,
OL,10,Fhaving put gloves on.
OL,12,F"You made no attempts to seek help.
OL,14,F"No sentence I can impose can put the
OL,15,Fclock back, nor should it be seen as
OL,16,Fany attempt to put a value on the loss
OL,17,Fof a human life.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G7/10
