OL,6,F"What was clear was by that Thursday,
OL,7,Fthe 20th of July, Sharon Gordon
OL,8,Fcontinued to criticise you as to the
OL,9,Fdelays and standard of your work. That
OL,10,Fclearly was the motivation for your
OL,11,Fanger.
OL,13,F"The principal aggravating factor is
OL,14,Fthis was a brutal and savage attack in
OL,15,Fthe victim's home, using a weapon. She
OL,16,Fwould have been no match for you.
OL,18,F"There was clearly an intention to
OL,19,Fkill."
