OL,6,FDetective Inspector Damian Forrest,
OL,7,Fwho led the investigation, said: "Mrs
OL,8,FGordon tragically lost her life
OL,9,Ffollowing a violent attack by Peter
OL,10,FNorgrove, which appears to have
OL,11,Fstemmed from him losing his temper
OL,12,Fafter a disagreement over the work he
OL,13,Fwas carrying out.
OL,15,F"Mrs Gordon's friends and family have
OL,16,Fbeen deeply affected by her death, and
OL,17,Fwhile Norgrove has now faced the
OL,18,Fconsequences of his appalling actions,
OL,19,Four thoughts remain with them as they
OL,20,Fcontinue to grieve."
